sentences: Masguda Islamovna Shamsutdinova (Tatar: Мәсгудә Ислам кызы Шәмсетдинова; born June 1, 1955 in Kshlau-Yelga, Bashkir ASSR) is a Tatar writer and composer.
She continued her studies at the Tatar History Institute and St. Petersburg State University and received a Ph. D in 2002.
